products.title: Lamborghini Diecast Model Car
products.description:
Product number : Lamborghini Aventador LOSLS501A


Type of diecast car : diecast already assembled
The diecast cars present on this site are 99% metal. Some diecast cars are made of resin and do not have openings such as the vehicles of the Ottomobile or GT Spirit brands. This diecast car is already assembled, it's not a model. So you can offer this Lamborghini Aventador diecast model cars directly without worrying about anything.


Scale : 1/43
When a diecast car is to scale 1/43, you can tell yourself that 1 centimeter on the diecast represents 43 on the real Lamborghini Aventador. Thus a diecast Lamborghini Aventador at 1/18 scale measures about 25 to 30 centimetres and a diecast car at 1/43 scale measures about 10 centimetres
